      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road! I've kept up with the maintenance, so it's all ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions; I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
