    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a purist\u2019s driver, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine known for its linear power delivery and characteristic boxer note. This unit has been meticulously maintained with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recently refreshed G96 six-speed manual transaxle that offers crisp, tactile gear selection. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a suspension overhaul including updated bushings and MacPherson struts, ensuring the rear-engine weight bias translates into incredible mechanical grip out of corners. The naturally aspirated induction provides immediate throttle response, while the cooling system has been pressure-tested for reliability. It is a mechanically sound example that prioritizes performance and structural integrity, perfect for the enthusiast seeking an analog connection to the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
