    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes an excellent balance between premium comfort and reliable performance. The exterior finish retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper\u2014honest marks of a car that has been driven and cared for. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather upholstery is clean and free of punctures, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every feature, from the responsive touchscreen infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control and heated seats, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a quiet, consistent engine idle. It has been meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history, including a recent oil change, fluid top-off, and a new set of brake pads installed just 500 miles ago. The tires possess significant tread depth, providing excellent grip and peace of mind for the seasons ahead. This is a well-sorted, dependable vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 32500.0,
